1. Download and install Elasticsearch on the same server or a separate machine that is hosting your website. Follow the instructions provided on the Elasticsearch official website: https://www.elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch

2. Create an index in Elasticsearch to hold the text messages and image descriptions that will be searched. You can create the index and its mapping using the Elasticsearch API or the Elasticsearch command-line interface. Here's an example mapping for your notes:

