      "properties": {
        "user_id": { "type": "keyword" },
        "message": { "type": "text" },
        "tags": { "type": "keyword" }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

3. Write a Python script to index the text messages and image descriptions in Elasticsearch whenever a new message is sent or an image is uploaded. This script should be run as a part of your backend server or using a separate jobs system like Celery.

